There is this code in UpdateDeleteSemanticAnalyzer
{noformat}
      // TODO: remove when this is enabled everywhere
75	      HiveConf.setBoolVar(conf, ConfVars.HIVE_VECTORIZATION_ROW_IDENTIFIER_ENABLED, true);
